description.value:
+10 to Fellowship Tests when interacting with Campaign Command or Imperial Nobility. Medals can't be acquired, only earned. Looks Like a Platinum Medallion encrusted with Gemstones.

Requirements

Distinguished Service Medal: Save an Important Imperial Official, Cleric, or Noble from the clutches of the Dark Eldar.

Effect: Special

Notes: -
